<paragraph blockId="3.[151,1437,152,526]" pageId="3" pageNumber="44">
Chaetotaxy: interval 
<number box="[442,457,190,216]" pageId="3" pageNumber="44" value="3.0">3</number>
of each elytron with 
<number box="[706,721,190,216]" pageId="3" pageNumber="44" value="4.0">4</number>
SP (first SP situated in stria 
<number box="[1057,1072,190,216]" pageId="3" pageNumber="44" value="3.0">3</number>
at first third of elytron, second SP laying in middle of interval 
<number box="[539,556,229,255]" pageId="3" pageNumber="44" value="3.0">3</number>
, at middle of elytron, and last two SP situated in stria 
<number box="[1229,1247,229,255]" pageId="3" pageNumber="44" value="2.0">2</number>
, in last third of elytron (third SP situated closer to forth SP than to second SP).
</paragraph>
